column5: Got word from person on the know. St Joe ice out was Monday, May 20. 30 days till we wet our lines...
Good, the ice auger can stay home. Looking forward to that first walleye dinner 6/22!
Good news! Talked to Dick on Sunday night and he thought it would early in the week. 10 days and we will be there. My son can't wait, he had a blast there last year.
